    "(2) Algorithms abstracted from human behavior or social phenomena.",
    "These models have strong learning ability and adaptability and have demonstrated excellent performance in image recognition and natural language processing fields.",
    "The Volleyball Premier League (VPL) (Moghdani and Salimifard 2018) is inspired by the rivalry and interaction between various volleyball teams throughout the season.",
    "The social learning behavior of humans arranged in families in the social environment is the basis for the Social Evolution and Learning Optimization (SELO) (Kumar et al. 2018) algorithm.",
    "The inspiration for Social Group Optimization (SGO) (Satapathy and Naik 2016) comes from social group learning."
